DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to investigate blood LDL-cholesterol and level of inflammatory markers after intake of food items with different fatty acid composition.
DOC.brief_title: Fat Quality on Blood Lipids and Immune Response
DOC.criteria: hsCRP < 10 mg/L total cholesterol 57.8 mmol/l(5070 y) total cholesterol 5.06.9 mmol/l (3049 y) total cholesterol 5.06.1 mmol/l (2529 y) LDLcholesterol at or above 3.5 mmol/l triglycerides at or lower 2.6 mmol/l BMI 2035 Stable bodyweight last 3 months. Chronic diseases fasting glucose > 6.0 mmol/l increased ASAT and ALAT medications affecting lipidmetabolism and inflammation
